import * as React from 'react';
import Grid from '@mui/material/Grid';
import {Box, Button, TextField, Typography} from '@mui/material';



export const MainPage =()=>{
  return(
    <Grid container
      sx={{ backgroundColor:'secondary.main', height:'100vh', width:'100vw', justifyContent:'center', alignItems:'center'}}>
      <Grid item container xs={12} justifyContent={'center'}  >

      <Grid item container xs={6} justifyContent={'center'} key={'generate'}  >
        <Grid item container xs={12} justifyContent={'center'} >
          <Typography variant={'h1'} textAlign={'center'}>
            {'Generate Token'}
          </Typography>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item container xs={12} justifyContent={'center'} sx={{marginTop:'10px'}} >
          <Box maxWidth="400px">
            <Typography variant={'h2'} style={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
              {'This section allows you to create a new token based on your chosen digits. Customize the available digits and click "Generate" to create a token.'}
            </Typography>
          </Box>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item container xs={12} justifyContent={'center'} marginTop={'50px'}  >
          <TextField  label="1-3-7-9" variant="outlined" sx={{width:'400px'}} />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item container xs={12} justifyContent={'center'} marginTop={'30px'} >
          <Button variant="contained" >Generate</Button>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>

        <Grid item container xs={6} justifyContent={'center'} key={'validate'}  >
          <Grid item container xs={12} justifyContent={'center'} >
            <Typography variant={'h3'} textAlign={'center'}>
              {'Validate Token'}
            </Typography>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item container xs={12} justifyContent={'center'} sx={{marginTop:'10px'}} >
            <Box maxWidth="400px">
              <Typography variant={'h2'} style={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
                {'Use this section to check the validity of a token using the Luhn algorithm. Enter the token and click "Validate" to see if it\'s a valid token.'}
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item container xs={12} justifyContent={'center'} marginTop={'50px'}  >
            <TextField  label="XXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX" variant="outlined" sx={{width:'400px'}} />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item container xs={12} justifyContent={'center'} marginTop={'30px'} >
            <Button variant="contained" >Validate</Button>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Grid>
  );
 }
